Product name: Vintage Trinity Cartier Ring Band with Rose, White, & Yellow Gold, VJ #655
Description:
Item Description:
Cartier has been making unique rings for decades, and this is no exception! There are three rings in one with this piece, which makes for an interesting accessory. The three ring bands are looped together in an effortless and invisible seam. When worn, the ring can be adjusted to numerous unique shapes and colors, depending on which band you want more visible. All the rings are made of 18k gold. The rose gold band has the hallmark "Cartier" written in cursive on the front. This is a great band to show your loved one your endless devotion!
The band has the engravings "KATHERINE" "TED" and "MICHAEL" written on each band inside the shank. This can be removed by us (for a small fee) upon request. The frames of the bands have very minor scratches but nothing too noticeable or damaging. This 1980s ring still remains in great condition! Each band is 3.5 mm.
This piece is accompanied with a V.G. appraisal certificate.
This piece shows that high quality craftsmanship will withstand the test of time!

Product name: Miracle Botanicals Organic Helichrysum Essential Oil - 100% Pure Helichrysum Gymnocephalum.....Free U.S. Shipping
Description:
- The Genus Helichrysum Family includes 500-600 Species throughout the World. The Highly Therapeutic Gymnocephalum Variety originates and grows Wild in Madagascar, where it is known as Rambiazina. Gymnocephalum scent is strong, fresh, camphorous, herbaceous and earthy.
- Botanical Name: Helichrysum Gymnocephalum
- Plant Part: Flowers
- Method of Extraction: Steam Distilled
- Country of Origin: Madagascar
- Color/Consistency: Clear color with thin consistency
- 5ml, 10ml, or 30ml in Amber Glass European Dropper Bottle
Helichrysum Gymnocephalum is a Middle Note Essential Oil with a Fresh, Clean, and Camphorous aroma. Helichrysum Gymnocephalum blends well with Cedarwood, Frankincense, Geranium, Lavender, Myrrh, Patchouli, Sandalwood, and Vetiver. 
Like most varieties of Helichrysum, Helichrysum Gymnocephalum differs significantly in chemical composition and therapeutic benefits. Helichrysum Gymnocephalum is an aromatic small yellow flower wildcrafted in Madagascar. 
Helichrysum Gymnocephalum essential oil is used in aromatherapy to heal the physical body through analgesic, antibacterial, anti-infectious, anti-inflammatory, antiseptic, antiviral, decongestant, expectorant, and toning properties.
